fields.description:
Android emulator is launching fine but my app is not exist their.
While debugging it is not showing any kind of error.

Please help me to resolve this non error issue.
I have recreate my emulator also cleaned the project and all other kind of stuff what i found on google first page at least.
fields.summary: App is not launching in android Simulator

comments.body:
There is not really much information to troubleshoot this issue. So lets do a couple of things -

1. Attach the output of the following command to make sure that your environment is setup correctly:
   titanium info

2. Try to build the project from command line and attach the output:
   titanium build -p android
Resolving this ticket as we cannot reproduce this issue and the requested information has not been provided.
